<img src="/HRDA/H1nW4QlAa.png" height=300>
</center>
</br>
<blockquote>
<p>Image from <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2204.13132" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Lukas Hoyer, Dengxin Dai, Luc Van Gool (2022)<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="related-works" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#related-works" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Related Works</h2>
<ul>
<li>Sematic Image Segmentation</li>
<li>Unsupervised Domain Adaptation (UDA)</li>
<li>Self-training</li>
<li>DAFormer</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="methodology" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#methodology" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Methodology</h2>
<h3 id="preliminary" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#preliminary" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Preliminary</h3>
<p>UDA 以 self-training 方法處理的大架構如下圖所示，由於過去的研究當中發現 Knowledge-Distillation 會對於 UDA 有正向的幫助，因此我們會訓練出一個 Student Network，依照 Source Label 以及 Target Pseudo-Label 去訓練，而 Teacher Network 則透過 Exponential Moving Average(EMA) 去更新。</p>
<center>
<img src="/HRDA/BJj4xy7R6.png" width=500>
</center>
</br>
<blockquote>
<p>Image from <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z9OJdaJ0i24&amp;ab_channel=LukasHoyer" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Lukas Hoyer's YouTube Channel<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></p>
</blockquote>
<p>這裡先定義一下接下來會用到的基本 Notation。</p>
