<p>Attention 可以告訴我們要考慮多少的 Context 以及多少的 Detail，於是把每個點跟 Attention 的值相乘，得到 Context 與 Detail 的結果後相加就會是 Fused 之後的預測結果。</p>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><msub><mover accent="true"><mi>y</mi><mo>^</mo></mover><mrow><mi>c</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>F</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mi>ζ</mi><mrow><mo fence="true">(</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><msubsup><mi>a</mi><mi>c</mi><mo mathvariant="normal" lspace="0em" rspace="0em">′</mo></msubsup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>⊙</mo><msub><mover accent="true"><mi>y</mi><mo>^</mo></mover><mi>c</mi></msub><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>s</mi><mo fence="true">)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>ζ</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msubsup><mi>a</mi><mi>c</mi><mo mathvariant="normal" lspace="0em" rspace="0em">′</mo></msubsup><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>s</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>⊙</mo><msubsup><mover accent="true"><mi>y</mi><mo>^</mo></mover><mi>d</mi><mo mathvariant="normal" lspace="0em" rspace="0em">′</mo></msubsup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
